TestAccountExecution_ExecuteBatch
└── given the Nexus account execution
    ├── when executing a batch operation
    │   └── it should execute successfully and increment the counter
    ├── when executing a batch operation with one action that reverts
    │   └── it should revert and the counter should remain unchanged
    ├── when executing an empty batch operation
    │   └── it should execute successfully with no changes
    ├── when executing a batch operation with value transfers
    │   └── it should transfer the correct amount of ETH to the receiver
    ├── when executing a batch operation with token transfers
    │   └── it should transfer the correct amount of tokens to the recipients
    ├── when executing a batch operation with separate approval and transfer
    │   └── it should approve and transfer the tokens correctly
    └── when executing a combined approval and transfer operation
        └── it should approve and transfer the tokens in a single operation
